{
  "stem": "1085.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Hungarian authorities, police, did not hurt the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were protecting the Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They did not deliver the Jews to Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If they found somebody who-- without documents, but who would identify himself that he is a Jew, the only reaction was get lost.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Get lost.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Policeman didn't want to have anything, but did not arrest him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Only later, Hungarians started [INAUDIBLE] police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1941, means to the German authorities in Poland?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I didn't know it. 1941?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My main mission was that organization-- the name was [NON-ENGLISH]-- had a candidate for the delegate of the government mainly.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were arguing the underground organizations have to be organized.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there should be some highest authority who would represent the Prime Minister residing in Paris and become a head of the underground struggle.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had a candidate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His name was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my job was to present all the arguments and convince General Sikorksi that he should appoint him immediately as delegate of the government.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, in that little organization I was sent by?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I saw over there no more than six-- six individuals.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the beginning, I was unaware.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everything was chaotic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time only, when we speak about the Jews, keep in mind that the time is important factor. 1939, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was no sign whatsoever of what was coming two years, three years later.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Jews only were-- I believe, by December that every Jew has to wear the Star of David.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Next, the Jews cannot publish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Jews cannot be MD's, cannot be doctors, cannot be lawyers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Jews cannot teach, cannot engage in public activities.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
